  <brief_title>Resection Location of Rectum in Laparoscopic Surgery for Slow Transit Constipation</brief_title>
  <official_title>High Resection vs. Low Resection of Rectum in Laparoscopic Total Colectomy for Slow Transit Constipation</official_title>
