  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study the recurrence rate of constipation after laparoscopic total colectomy with high&#xD;
      resection or low resection of rectum&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are going to study the recurrence rate of constipation after laparoscopic&#xD;
      total colectomy with high resection or low resection of rectum. High resection is defined as&#xD;
      resection at 12~15cm from anus and low resection as 6~8cm.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
